1. Software & Database Requirements
    Database Management System (DBMS):
    MySQL / PostgreSQL(recommended) / SQL Server
    SQLite (For lightweight usage)

2. Data Visualization Tools (Optional for Dashboards):
    Power BI
    Tableau
    Python (Matplotlib, Seaborn)

3. SQL Query Editor:

    MySQL Workbench
    pgAdmin 4 (For PostgreSQL)
    DBeaver / DataGrip (** Universal SQL Editors)

4. Dataset Requirements
    eCommerce Dataset (initial)
    Dataset Fields: order_id, customer_id, product_id, order_date, total_amount, payment_method, category, region, etc.
    Cleaned Data File: (final) after removing/filling null values                           
